{"primaryContentSections":[{"declarations":[{"platforms":["macOS"],"tokens":[{"kind":"keyword","text":"func"},{"text":" ","kind":"text"},{"kind":"identifier","text":"set"},{"kind":"text","text":"("},{"text":"timeout","kind":"externalParam"},{"kind":"text","text":": "},{"preciseIdentifier":"s:Si","kind":"typeIdentifier","text":"Int"},{"text":")","kind":"text"}],"languages":["swift"]}],"kind":"declarations"},{"kind":"content","content":[{"text":"Discussion","anchor":"discussion","level":2,"type":"heading"},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"On a blocking socket, this means that any blocking "},{"isActive":true,"type":"reference","identifier":"doc:\/\/GIO\/documentation\/GIO\/Socket"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"operation will time out after "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"timeout"},{"text":" seconds of inactivity,","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"text":"returning ","type":"text"},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"timedOut"},{"text":".","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"On a non-blocking socket, calls to ","type":"text"},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"g_socket_condition_wait()"},{"type":"text","text":" will"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"also fail with "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"timedOut"},{"type":"text","text":" after the given time. Sources"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":"created with "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"g_socket_create_source()"},{"text":" will trigger after","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"timeout"},{"text":" seconds of inactivity, with the requested condition","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"set, at which point calling "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"g_socket_receive()"},{"type":"text","text":", "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"g_socket_send()"},{"type":"text","text":","},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"code":"g_socket_check_connect_result()","type":"codeVoice"},{"text":", etc, will fail with","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"timedOut"},{"type":"text","text":"."}]},{"inlineContent":[{"text":"If ","type":"text"},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"timeout"},{"text":" is 0 (the default), operations will never time out","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"text":"on their own.","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Note that if an I\/O operation is interrupted by a signal, this may"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"cause the timeout to be reset."}]}]}],"abstract":[{"text":"Sets the time in seconds after which I\/O operations on ","type":"text"},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"socket"},{"text":" will","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"time out if they have not yet completed."}],"variants":[{"traits":[{"interfaceLanguage":"swift"}],"paths":["\/documentation\/gio\/socket\/set(timeout:)"]}],"metadata":{"symbolKind":"method","externalID":"s:3GIO14SocketProtocolPAAE3set7timeoutySi_tF::SYNTHESIZED::s:3GIO6SocketC","role":"symbol","modules":[{"name":"GIO"}],"extendedModule":"GIO","title":"set(timeout:)","fragments":[{"kind":"keyword","text":"func"},{"text":" ","kind":"text"},{"text":"set","kind":"identifier"},{"text":"(","kind":"text"},{"kind":"externalParam","text":"timeout"},{"kind":"text","text":": "},{"text":"Int","kind":"typeIdentifier","preciseIdentifier":"s:Si"},{"text":")","kind":"text"}],"roleHeading":"Instance Method"},"kind":"symbol","identifier":{"url":"doc:\/\/GIO\/documentation\/GIO\/Socket\/set(timeout:)","interfaceLanguage":"swift"},"hierarchy":{"paths":[["doc:\/\/GIO\/documentation\/GIO","doc:\/\/GIO\/documentation\/GIO\/Socket","doc:\/\/GIO\/documentation\/GIO\/Socket\/SocketProtocol-Implementations"]]},"sections":[],"schemaVersion":{"minor":3,"patch":0,"major":0},"references":{"doc://GIO/documentation/GIO/Socket/SocketProtocol-Implementations":{"url":"\/documentation\/gio\/socket\/sock